cs.RO, cs.MA, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper deals with the problem of exploring unknown and dynamic environments using a decentralized multi-robot system, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of a swarm of robots and the coordination among them suggest the involvement of multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and control systems (cs.SY). The exploration and mapping of the environment require the use of artificial intelligence techniques (cs.AI), and the wall-climbing units may involve computer vision (cs.CV) for navigation and obstacle avoidance.
